  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Sirius is in a great location close to the centre of Taormina. The small traditional villa has beautiful Sicilian décor and the rooms all have balconies. When you're not lounging beside the infinity pool, get out and explore the nearby beaches or take a day trip to other parts of <a data-udi="umb://document/b037a20c14a3421ba33b32859c9e3344" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b037a20c14a3421ba33b32859c9e3344}" title="Sicily">Sicily</a>. </p>]]></listingDescription>
